bio	"Meteorologist Dr. Nick Palisch is a weather communicator, storm chaser, and educator with a passion for helping communities better understand the atmosphere and the science behind severe weather. He holds a Bachelor's degree in Atmospheric Science with an emphasis in severe storms and has spent years studying and tracking impactful weather across the Midwest, including Missouri and Illinois.\n\nKnown for his relatable and educational forecasting style, Dr. Palisch combines meteorological science with public awareness to make complex weather information easier to understand. Through his First Warn Weather platform, writing, and community outreach, he focuses on severe weather preparedness, winter storms, climate patterns, and everyday weather education while maintaining a strong commitment to public safety and communication."
